description:
This is a 21 minute workout called '20 minutes of FAT BURNING FUN! | Intense Indoor Cycling Workout' from the channel Kaleigh Cohen Cycling.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: 20 minutes is all you need to get closer to your goals, get an amazing workout, and improve your overall health! This cycling workout includes intense climbs, sprints, and jogs for a seriously awesome burn! Get ready to have FUN and reach your goals! Let's do this!

IMPORTANT! The RPMs noted throughout the ride are just a range! Make sure to ride where you feel comfortable! That may be above or below the range indicated.
